reagent-name-purge = purge
reagent-name-strong-heart-brew = strongheart brew
reagent-name-warriors-blood = warrior's blood tonic
reagent-name-murder-draught = murder draught

reagent-desc-purge = A chemical that flushes many mind altering substances from the bloodstream.
reagent-desc-strong-heart-brew = A compound that clears poison and encourages circulation, but only in exceptionally cold circulatory systems
reagent-desc-warriors-blood = A compound that rapidly increases tissue regeneration, healing burns, punctures and slashes rapidly.
reagent-desc-murder-draught = A culturally sacred compound, highly illegal in Auroran space. It rapidly regenerates even the most grievous wounds while enhancing reaction speeds for the user, though it has a toxifying effect on the liver.
